==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Questionary
<hw>Ques"tion*a*ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who makes it
his business to seek after relics and carry them about for
sale.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A set of questions for submission to a group of
persons for the purpose of bringing out their resemblances and
differences in the matter considered. The <xex>questionary method</xex>
is a recognized form of psychological investigation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Questioner</ent>⟦br⟧
